data.title: Wells Fargo (WFC) Return on Assets ROA from the second quarter of 2024 to second quarter of 2023 and for the year 2024, Average High and Low, Fundamental Ratios from Jun 30 2024 to Jun 30 2023
meta_keywords: Wells Fargo Return on Assets ROA results by quarter and year
data.meta_description: In its second quarter of 2024, Wells Fargo And Company yielded a return on asset (ROA) of 0.96% Meanwhile, within the Financial sector 354 other companies had a higher return on assets.
data.text: In the fiscal year 2023 ROA improved to 0.99 % compared to prior year, due to annual net income growth of 42.82 % to $19,255.00 million, while value of Wells Fargo's overall assets grew just by 2.62 % to $1,940,976.00 million, compared to $1,940,976.00 a year before.
